Pretty sure this wolf fell in love with me (and the feeling was definitely mutual). I spent the afternoon at @apexprotectionproject -
If you’re in California I highly recommend checking ‘em out! I’ve always had a fascination with wolves but wow, getting that close and spending this kinda time with these gentle giants, really blew my mind. I hate how hollywood has villainized them. There is nothing quite like looking deep into the eyes of a wolf. It was magic. They are magic. I feel really lucky. 🐺

So… not gonna lie! I was nervous. But then I realized this is a just a photo shoot of all my organs!  Easy peasy! (It actually was. I laid still and watched Netflix for an hour.) So, here’s the deal, Prenuvo uses advanced MRI to perform a full body scan able to detect solid cancerous tumors at stage 1 and around 500 other conditions (including aneurysms, spine herniations, digestive issues, fatty liver disease). During preventative screenings 95% of the cancers and medical conditions found are at an early stage, where treatment is easier and much more likely to be successful. Unlike other screening mechanisms, Prenuvo does not use radiation or contrast, making it a safe preventative screening tool.
Prenuvo’s goal is to shift the healthcare system from reactive to proactive by empowering its patients with incredible health insights and taking the guesswork out of healthcare. I always have a lot of worries… hoping this eases my mind for awhile. Thank you @prenuvo ❤️ (I get my results in a couple weeks and I’ll share more then!) Im really grateful that this kind of preventative care/screening is accessible for me. I hope that one day insurance recognizes that these kinds of screens are important, life saving and (ultimately could be) money saving for them in the future and will start covering this kind of thing! They offered me a code - SARARUE for 300 off. (Im not being paid, though I did get a discount on my scan. I just really like this technology.)
I just love this little thing so much. 💜🦄🥳

Ok. This is awesome. My @yardzen designs are dope!!! So, I started working with them last year... I was really curious about them after stalking some insta stories and (full disclosure) reached out to partner. I wanted a more modern clean look to our front yard, backyard and entry way... And now (if Hollywood ever gets to go back to work and if I ever have a job again🤪😭😬) making these designs a reality will be my next project! Working with Yardzen was fairly easy. You send em pics, tell em what you like and they make your design dreams come true! You zoom a few times with your designer to get all the details right and they just send pics with a list of paint colors and plants and full set of plans. Highly recommend - 10 out of 10!!!! (I plan to save money on labor by making my children do all the planting 🤣😂🤣 #motheroftheyear )
